br />\n你老細真係無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e734e7997abfa8c97c306648e7aba4d6b9122a3a","tid":440873,"uid":100982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"收數佬禁鐘<br />\n收： 唔該陳生丫<br />\n我： 咩事<br />\n收： 終於肯認啦咩 又話搵錯人無呢個人 屌你老母丫 還錢未呀<br />\n我： 你on99定食撚錯藥呀 姓陳就係叫陳大文咩 hi撚大左去睇醫生啦屌你老母<br />\n佢： 丫屌你老母又唔撚認 下刪好多粗口<br />\n我： 你唔撚信就罷 答你都哂鳩氣 <br />\n跟住刪番門 條木咀就走左<br />\n利申番 開左木門無開鐵閘先夠膽屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔是我差人錢"},{"pid":"86c0e33915570dadcd3e834c52a669124cda1938","tid":440873,"uid":143945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩過電話，上門，wtsapp grp，貼街招<br />\n由細搬到大，由淆底到直接打去講數都試過<br />\n真係好好嘅磨練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打上你公司,貼哂成個走廊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得有次我煮緊飯有人拍門,我拎住把刀去開門,個人一開口我屌你..........跟住跑走左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試過，整緊野揸住支大士巴拿踢拖開門<br />\n我話無哩個人，佢就打搞哂咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b59d1be217fa88ca162cbfab4897f76d65c3547","tid":440873,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:02:44.000Z","msg":"試過有個收數佬好on9,係我小學果陣,打去我學校,<br />\n一開頭佢話係我老豆,叫我快d呃老師有事要走,返屋企,<br />\n但係某商場等佢....我比左個電話老師,真係早走左<br />\n<br />\n去左睇玩具,公園玩,玩到放學時間夠鐘返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553465e10534c87c5f502399481cb6a8699a1383","tid":440873,"uid":33809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s